de.com.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E5%88%B0%E6%88%91%E5%80%91%E7%9A%84%E7%B6%B2%E7%AB%99www.help4suicide.com.hk&d=40Eeu%2FLL1847%2FNonScroNedgoykoOisTuuABwIAScok%3D&h=4aaa5293\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">到我們的網站www.help4suicide.com.hk</a>。 那裡有一些勵志故事和有趣短片，你可以隨心看看。你也可以進入網站內的『Chat窿』（星期一至五：上午六時至凌晨一時；星期六、日及公眾假期：下午８時至凌晨１時），讓我們的義工為你加油打氣！<br />\n<br />\n我們願意聆聽你的心聲，伴你一起走過這段艱難的時候！只因『晴天雨天要樂天，難關難過總會過』！<br />\n<br />\n《自殺．自療．互助舍》"},{"pid":"a39931e70f06e4ddd0acfc9dbed65c9af6b2855b","tid":1697182,"uid":131721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"01af03032df10976d0b3bb408ded7f12685a40dc","tid":1697182,"uid":224528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T16:22:06.000Z","msg":"收手啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T15:52:35.000Z","msg":"幾努力都感動不了不愛你的人！<br />\n正如永遠都叫不醒裝睡的人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}